text: Prokoeneniidae is a family of microscorpions in the order Palpigradi. There are at least two genera and about seven described species in Prokoeneniidae. ==Genera== * Prokoenenia Borner, 1901 * Triadokoenenia Condé, 1991 ==References== ==Further reading== * * * Category:Palpigradi
title: Prokoeneniidae
